    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">-&gt; -&gt; DXF Layers</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">CAD-Line &gt; DXF tab &gt; DXF Layers</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="VariableName">DXF-Drawings</text> frequently use<text styleclass="VariableName"> Layers</text> for different drawing information. </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Use the <text styleclass="Interface">DXF Layers dialog</text> to show or hide each Layer in a <text styleclass="VariableName">DXF-Drawing</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">To open the <text styleclass="Interface">DXF Layers dialog</text>:</para>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">Click</text> the<text style="font-style:italic;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Edit Layers</text><text style="font-style:italic;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text">button</text> in the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-CADLine-DXF">CAD-Line dialog &gt; DXF tab</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_"><anchor id="CADLine-DXFLayers"><keywords><keyword>DXF Layers<keyword>Colors</keyword><keyword>Show / Hide</keyword></keyword></keywords></anchor>DXF Layers dialog</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:237px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-Dialog-CADLine-DXF-Layers-A.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">To Show or Hide a Layer:</para>
          <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text style="font-style:normal;">Click</text> a <image src="MD-OK-smallest.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Body Text"> (or </text><image src="MD-CROSS.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text">) in the</text>&#32;<text styleclass="VariableName">Show</text> column<text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text style="font-style:normal;">Click</text> the <text styleclass="VariableName">Layer Visible</text> (or <text styleclass="VariableName">Layer Hidden</text>) check-box</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="VariableName">To change the color of a Layer:</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">This option does not work!</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">See <text styleclass="VariableName">Solid Color</text> in the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-CADLine-DXF">DXF tab</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
